data.eml:eml: Two new species of the genus Leeonychiurus Sun & Arbea, 2014 (Collembola: Onychiuridae) from Korea

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Park, Kyung-Hwa (2017): Two new species of the genus Leeonychiurus Sun & Arbea, 2014 (Collembola: Onychiuridae) from Korea. Zootaxa 4329 (3): 292-300, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4329.3.7
